  "id": 1,
  "nama": "Audit IT - Revised",
  "deskripsi": "Pemeriksaan sistem TI perusahaan (update)",
  "harga": 3500000
}
```

### âœ… Response

``` json
{
  "status": "success",
  "message": "Data berhasil diperbarui"
}
```

## 4. ğŸ—‘ï¸ Delete Data

**Endpoint:** `/delete.php`\
**Method:** `DELETE`\
**Deskripsi:** Menghapus data berdasarkan `id`.

### ğŸ”§ Request Body (JSON)

